{"tid":1639486,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"建築物歷史碑石唔好搞！！！","createTime":"2019-10-08T15:33:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-09T04:09:22.000Z","uid":77905,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0b9456d72b9828db593c6d5d70bb5e754c345c9e","tid":1639486,"uid":77905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T15:33:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AKYCqdv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAKYCqdv.jpg&h=4f0f353d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n康文署大樓原為區域市政局大樓，一九八九年十月三十日由港督衛奕信爵士主持奠基。圖為奠基石原貌。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eWUmRTw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeWUmRTw.jpg&h=226b4c10&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n區域市政局大樓於一九九一年九月廿六日由港督衛奕信爵士揭幕，圖為揭幕碑記原貌。九九年殺局前，大樓是區局議事廳所在地。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YT7okMR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYT7okMR.jpg&h=a7948ffb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n近日焦點所在的港鐵沙田站，有碑石紀念代理港督夏鼎基爵士於一九八二年五月六日主持九廣鐵路第一期近郊電氣化火車啟用典禮。圖為碑石原貌。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/C5NGRTx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC5NGRTx.jpg&h=b9fb9c66&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九龍政府合署，位於地下的九龍中央郵局是於一九六七年八月十日由署理輔政司何禮文在郵政司高旭陪同下主持啟用典禮的。大樓水牌和地下郵局內部裝修，相信仍大致保留當年佈局，甚具六十年代的殖民地風味。留意水牌的中文字仍是按舊式由右至左排列，而非現今由左至右排列。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">呢啲唔好搞</span>"},{"pid":"3fc3963b89af399efc48d95810615ea8b324fbd2","tid":1639486,"uid":182519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T15:36:12.000Z","msg":"國際文宣組全面進化，大型國際文宣活動&quot;What if they own it&quot;<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1639378\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1639378</a>"},{"pid":"4d898127fb0fe76a496e30c08cdc9d6b0ad20c8a","tid":1639486,"uid":77905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T16:33:15.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"dfd24825fce384402a438ecb47e48f8fd8b8ccb0","tid":1639486,"uid":94771,"like":0,"disli